{
  "stem": "19195.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Once I saw a lady looking through the fence where the kids were playing on, you know, on a sunny day.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this lady somehow passed out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was on the other side of the fence.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the kids were very sad, because she didn't come to look for them, look at them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I just never forgot those kids.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Can I skip a little bit?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, I'd like to try to keep it in the sequence.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So how long did you remain in the orphanage?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "13 months.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A neighbor-- we didn't have a telephone there, but a neighbor told me that I could use the phone any time I want to call my parents.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was very lonely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I missed them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went a few times.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then one day, we heard what's coming up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we heard that they take away-- they took [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took so far away the-- the Jews from Slovakia, from the Czech countries.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And our country-- where I was born, Bilky, became Hungary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in order for us to be able to survive from Bilky, we needed to prove that, you know, we are Jews, and we do live in Hungary, which wasn't true.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that's-- that's how they, you know, let it go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Next, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what do you call those people that-- [PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] I was-- I went to order the-- in the grocery store, what we needed.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I came back, a friend of mine came there, and she said, so you're gonna stay in Budapest?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, I'm gonna stay, because they're gonna take us away to Poland somewhere.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, aren't you coming home to your parents?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
